Re: Windows 7 Lost functionality
by Harisenbon » Wed 12.02.2009 9:59 pm I'll have to check my version, but I'm pretty sure mine will support JP Handwriting (as it's the JP version )If it *didn't* support it, I'd be worried. *laugh*
